<item>
            <title>[SPARK-45057] Deadlock caused by rdd replication level of 2</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-45057</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
When 2 tasks try to compute same rdd with replication level of 2 and running on only 2 executors. Deadlock will happen.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Task only release lock after writing into local machine and replicate to remote executor.&lt;/p&gt;

